Docs.summary: Class representing Credential subtree in the PerProviderSubscription (PPS) Management Object (MO) tree.

remarks.para: Class representing Credential subtree in the PerProviderSubscription (PPS) Management Object (MO) tree. For more info, refer to Hotspot 2.0 PPS MO defined in section 9.1 of the Hotspot 2.0 Release 2 Technical Specification.
In addition to the fields in the Credential subtree, this will also maintain necessary information for the private key and certificates associated with this credential.

Docs.summary: Get the minimum TLS version for TLS-based EAP methods. -or- Set the minimum TLS version for TLS-based EAP methods.

remarks.para: Property getter documentation:
Get the minimum TLS version for TLS-based EAP methods.
Property setter documentation:

Set the minimum TLS version for TLS-based EAP methods.
android.net.wifi.WifiManager#isTlsMinimumVersionSupported() indicates whether or not a minimum TLS version can be set. If not supported, the minimum TLS version is always TLS v1.0.
android.net.wifi.WifiManager#isTlsV13Supported() indicates whether or not TLS v1.3 is supported. If requested minimum is not supported, it will default to the maximum supported version.
